== 生平 ==
枪击案杀手为29岁的美国公民奥马尔·马丁，是一名[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，出生于[[纽约|纽约]]，其父母为[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]移民。<ref name="dm3637414">{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3637414/Everyone-running-Gunman-bursts-gay-nightclub-Florida-shoots-20-people-taking-hostages.html|title=Orlando shooting at Pulse is worst mass shooting in history with at least 50 dead|date=2016-06-12|work=Daily Mail Online|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308052953/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3637414/Everyone-running-Gunman-bursts-gay-nightclub-Florida-shoots-20-people-taking-hostages.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方怀疑枪手与伊斯兰极端宗教组织有关联，凶手过去也曾自称和“恐怖组织”有联系。<ref>{{cite news|title=Mass shooting at Pulse nightclub in Orlando, Florida|date=2016-06-12|work=The Australian|accessdate=|quote=The FBI has described the shooting as -{‘an act of terrorism’’}- and say they suspect the shooter had ties to radical Islam.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dailycaller.com/2016/06/12/fbi-suspect-bragged-about-ties-to-terrorist-organizations/|accessdate=2016-06-12|date=2016-06-12|last=|first=|publisher=The Daily Caller|script-title=en:FBI: Suspect Bragged About Ties To ‘Terrorist Organizations’|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308020009/https://dailycaller.com/2016/06/12/fbi-suspect-bragged-about-ties-to-terrorist-organizations/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《商业内幕》（Business Insider）报道称该恐怖袭击为“独狼式恐怖袭击”，没有证据显示奥马尔曾经直接受过IS组织的领导和训练，而是响应了IS“在各国就地发动圣战处决[[卡菲勒|卡菲勒]]”的号召。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/isis-statement-orlando-shooting-attack-2016-6/|title=Islamic terrorism tie eyed in Orlando gay bar shooting|accessdate=2016-06-12|publisher=|archive-date=2018-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824112931/https://www.businessinsider.com/isis-statement-orlando-shooting-attack-2016-6|dead-url=no}}</ref>

奧馬爾的父親在接受媒體採訪時称兒子行凶的动机并非出于伊斯兰信仰，而是於數月前在[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]看到兩名男子在自己妻兒面前接吻後，感到非常憤怒。<ref name="dm3637414" />

奧馬爾本人疑為一名[[同性戀者|同性戀者]]，舊同學指曾邀請他一同到同性戀夜店。在事發夜店的一名表演者表示，他在3年前曾光顧過該夜店，並與另一男子跳舞。他還曾透過同性戀交友程式和[[同性戀者|同性戀者]]結交。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/former-classmates-recall-orlando-shooters-bizarre-reaction-on-911/2016/06/13/f08b2950-3187-11e6-95c0-2a6873031302_story.html|title=Orlando gunman had been seen on gay dating apps, at Pulse nightclub before shooting|date=2016-06-13|publisher=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809013523/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/former-classmates-recall-orlando-shooters-bizarre-reaction-on-911/2016/06/13/f08b2950-3187-11e6-95c0-2a6873031302_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3639961/Orlando-terrorist-went-gay-club-Pulse-dozen-times-got-drunk-belligerent-talked-wife-kid-massacring-49-people-there.html|title=Omar Mateen was gay, says ex-wife and former friend: Orlando terrorist used homosexual dating app and visited Pulse at least a dozen times|date=2016-06-13|publisher=[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224185426/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3639961/Orlando-terrorist-went-gay-club-Pulse-dozen-times-got-drunk-belligerent-talked-wife-kid-massacring-49-people-there.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 枪击案和死亡 ==
{{main article|2016年奥兰多夜店枪击案}}
這次襲擊是美國歷史上最嚴重的槍擊案{{efn|之前最嚴重的槍擊案是2007年的[[維吉尼亞理工大學校園槍擊案|維吉尼亞理工大學校園槍擊案]]<ref name="LATimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-orlando-nightclub-shooting-20160612-snap-story.html|title=Fifty dead in Orlando gay nightclub shooting, worst mass killing in U.S. history; gunman reportedly pledged allegiance to Islamic State|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate= 2016-06-12| date= 2016-06-12}}</ref>}}，也是美國歷史上最嚴重的[[LGBT迫害|LGBT迫害]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Mark Joseph|last=Stern|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/outward/2016/06/12/pulse_nightclub_shooting_and_tragic_history_of_violence_at_lgbtq_clubs_in.html|title=The Long, Tragic History of Violence at LGBTQ Bars and Clubs in America|work=Slate|date=2016-06-12|accessdate=2016-06-12|archive-date=2016-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612172215/http://www.slate.com/blogs/outward/2016/06/12/pulse_nightclub_shooting_and_tragic_history_of_violence_at_lgbtq_clubs_in.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而且是美國本土自[[九一一襲擊事件|九一一襲擊事件]]以来最严重的恐怖襲擊。<ref name="cnn">{{cite news |url= http://www.cnn.com/2016/06/12/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting/index.html |title= 50 killed in Florida nightclub, shooter pledged ISIS allegiance |first= Ashley |last= Fantz |first2= Faith |last2= Karimi |first3= Eliott C. |last3= McLaughlin |publisher= CNN |date= 2016-06-12 |accessdate= 2016-06-12 |archive-date= 2019-05-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190525135958/https://www.cnn.com/2016/06/12/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting/index.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=The Orlando attack could transform the picture of post-9/11 terrorism in America|first=Ann|last=Swanson|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/wonk/wp/2016/06/12/the-orlando-attack-could-transform-the-picture-of-post-911-terrorism-in-america/|date=2016-06-12|accessdate=2016-06-12|work=The Washington Post|archive-date=2016-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612203733/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/wonk/wp/2016/06/12/the-orlando-attack-could-transform-the-picture-of-post-911-terrorism-in-america/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

这次发生在[[脉冲夜店|脉冲夜店]]的枪案共造成包括杀手在内至少50人死亡，53人受伤（包括52位平民和1名警官），多名伤者伤势严重，在当地医院接受手术。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/06/orlando-nightclub-shooting/486713/|title=Orlando Nightclub Attack: What We Know|accessdate=2016-06-12|date=2016-06-12|publisher=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]]|first1=Krishnadev|last1=Calamur|first2=Matt|last2=Ford|archive-date=2016-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612151926/http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/06/orlando-nightclub-shooting/486713/|dead-url=no}}</ref>事发的夜店距离奥兰多地区医疗中心仅仅三个街区的距离，大部分伤员均被送往該医院。<ref name="NYTInitial">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/13/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting.html|title=Shooting at Orlando Nightclub Kills 50, Police Say|last=Alvarez|first=Lizette|date=2016-06-12|last2=Kenny|first2=Steve|newspaper=New York Times|accessdate=2016-06-12|last3=Pérez-Peña|first3=Richard|authorlink3=Richard Pérez-Peña|archive-date=2016-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612102027/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/13/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

